---
// SPDX-License-Identifier: AGPL-3.0-or-later
// PersonaCards.astro — developer-first hierarchy.
// Tier 0: one spotlight Developer card (dark terminal, full width) — the core ICP.
// Tier 1: Consultant + CEO/PM (secondary, high-value).
// Tier 2: BA/Sales + Marketer (the whole team benefits).
// All "See examples" CTAs route to the real /examples showcase.
---

<!-- Tier 0 · Developer spotlight (the primary audience) -->
<article
  class="cv-reveal group relative mt-12 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-viindoo-primary/25 bg-viindoo-bg-1 shadow-lift"
  data-testid="persona-card-developer"
>
  <div class="cv-aurora-field opacity-60" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_1fr]">
    <!-- Pitch -->
    <div class="p-8 sm:p-10">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
        <span class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-viindoo-primary/15 text-viindoo-primary-bright ring-1 ring-viindoo-primary/30">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="16,18 22,12 16,6"/><polyline points="8,6 2,12 8,18"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <p class="cv-kicker text-viindoo-primary-bright">Built for developers</p>
        <span class="ml-auto hidden sm:inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-viindoo-primary/30 bg-viindoo-primary/10 px-2.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-viindoo-primary-bright">Primary</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-viindoo-on-dark leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Stop guessing field names.<br />Trace any override in one call.
      </h3>
      <p class="mt-4 text-viindoo-on-dark-muted leading-relaxed max-w-[46ch]">
        Resolve any model, field, or method across versions and modules. Find the exact
        override point. Catch deprecations before you upgrade &mdash; grounded in a real
        inheritance graph, not a guess.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-6 gap-y-3">
        <a href="/examples" class="group/cta inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-viindoo-primary-bright">
          See it resolve, live
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover/cta:translate-x-1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/bootstrap" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-viindoo-on-dark-dim hover:text-viindoo-on-dark transition">Bootstrap &amp; SCSS by Odoo version &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Terminal proof -->
    <div class="relative border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-white/8 bg-viindoo-bg-0/70 p-6 sm:p-8 font-mono text-[12.5px] leading-relaxed">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-4 text-viindoo-on-dark-dim">
        <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#FF5F57]"></span>
        <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#FEBC2E]"></span>
        <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#27C93F]"></span>
        <span class="ml-2 text-[11px]">odoo-semantic</span>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-1 text-viindoo-on-dark-muted">
        <div><span class="text-viindoo-primary-bright">&gt;_</span> find_override_point(sale.order, action_confirm)</div>
        <div class="text-viindoo-on-dark">&rarr; 4 hooks across 3 modules · 312 tokens</div>
        <div class="text-viindoo-success">&#10003; sale_stock · _action_confirm() &middot; super() preserved</div>
        <div class="pt-3"><span class="text-viindoo-primary-bright">&gt;_</span> resolve_field(sale.order, partner_id, v=17.0)</div>
        <div class="text-viindoo-on-dark">&rarr; res.partner · required · defined_in: sale</div>
        <div class="text-viindoo-success">&#10003; verified against Neo4j index</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <span class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-[3px] origin-left scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500 bg-gradient-to-r from-viindoo-primary to-viindoo-secondary rounded-t-3xl"></span>
</article>

<!-- Tier 1 · Secondary, high-value workflows -->
<div class="cv-reveal grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">

  <!-- Consultant -->
  <article
    class="persona-card group relative rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-viindoo-success"
    data-testid="persona-card-consultant"
  >
    <div class="mb-5 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-viindoo-success/10 text-viindoo-success">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
        <polygon points="16.24,7.76 14.12,14.12 7.76,16.24 9.88,9.88"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-viindoo-success-deep mb-3">For Consultants</p>
    <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-viindoo-dark mb-2 leading-tight">Fit/gap in 30 minutes. Not 2 days.</h3>
    <p class="text-viindoo-body text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Map 50 requirements against standard Odoo coverage instantly. Know what&apos;s already built, what extends what, which version delivers what.</p>
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-viindoo-muted bg-gray-50 rounded p-3 border-l-2 border-viindoo-success">
      <span class="text-viindoo-success-deep font-semibold">&gt;_</span> check_module_exists(loyalty, v=17.0) → ✓ sale_loyalty (CE) · 43 tk
    </div>
    <a href="/examples" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-viindoo-success-deep group-hover:gap-2 transition">See examples →</a>
    <span class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-[3px] origin-left scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300 bg-viindoo-success rounded-t-2xl"></span>
  </article>

  <!-- CEO / PM -->
  <article
    class="persona-card group relative rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-viindoo-secondary"
    data-testid="persona-card-pm"
  >
    <div class="mb-5 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-viindoo-secondary/10 text-viindoo-secondary">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M3 3v18h18M7 14l3-3 4 4 5-5"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-viindoo-secondary mb-3">For CEOs &amp; PMs</p>
    <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-viindoo-dark mb-2 leading-tight">Measure blast radius before greenlight.</h3>
    <p class="text-viindoo-body text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Quantify upgrade risk. See how many modules depend on a field you want to change. Make data-driven decisions on what to refactor.</p>
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-viindoo-muted bg-gray-50 rounded p-3 border-l-2 border-viindoo-secondary">
      <span class="text-viindoo-secondary font-semibold">&gt;_</span> impact_analysis(sale.order, amount_total) → 12 mods · 38 refs · 3,218 tk
    </div>
    <a href="/examples" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-viindoo-secondary group-hover:gap-2 transition">See examples →</a>
    <span class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-[3px] origin-left scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300 bg-viindoo-secondary rounded-t-2xl"></span>
  </article>

</div>

<!-- Tier 2 divider -->
<div class="cv-reveal mt-10 mb-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm font-mono text-viindoo-muted uppercase tracking-widest">
  <span>And the whole team benefits</span>
  <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gray-200"></span>
</div>

<!-- Tier 2: 2 compact cards -->
<div class="cv-reveal grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

  <!-- BA / Sales -->
  <article
    class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 transition hover:border-viindoo-warning flex gap-5"
    data-testid="persona-card-sales"
  >
    <div class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-viindoo-warning/10 text-viindoo-warning">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-viindoo-warning-deep mb-1">For BA / Sales</p>
      <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-viindoo-dark mb-1 leading-tight">Answer the prospect before they hang up.</h3>
      <p class="text-viindoo-body text-sm leading-snug">Confirm capability claims with evidence — real module names, real field paths.</p>
      <a href="/examples" class="mt-2 inline-block text-xs font-semibold text-viindoo-warning-deep">See examples →</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Marketer -->
  <article
    class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 transition hover:border-viindoo-info flex gap-5"
    data-testid="persona-card-marketer"
  >
    <div class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-viindoo-info/10 text-viindoo-info">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M3 11l18-5v12L3 14M11.6 16.8a3 3 0 1 1-5.8-1.6"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-viindoo-info-deep mb-1">For Marketers</p>
      <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-viindoo-dark mb-1 leading-tight">Turn version diffs into marketing copy.</h3>
      <p class="text-viindoo-body text-sm leading-snug">Diff features across versions, generate marketing-friendly summaries anchored in truth.</p>
      <a href="/examples" class="mt-2 inline-block text-xs font-semibold text-viindoo-info-deep">See examples →</a>
    </div>
  </article>

</div>
